    <legend>Navigation Groups</legend>
    <div class="tile fg-anthilla-blu">Group 1: Blacklist</div>
    <div class="tile fg-anthilla-blu">Group 2: Contents</div>
    <div class="tile fg-anthilla-blu">Group 3: Open</div>
    <div class="tile fg-anthilla-blu" style="margin-bottom: 120px;">Apply Config</div>
    <br />
    <legend>Group Membership</legend>
    <div class="tab-control" data-role="tab-control">
        <ul class="tabs">
            <li class="active"><a href="#_grpmmb_">Group Membership</a></li>
            <li><a href="#_flip_">Filter-less IP</a></li>
            <li><a href="#_flus_">Filter-less Users</a></li>
            <li><a href="#_waip_">IP w/out Web Access</a></li>
            <li><a href="#_waus_">Users w/out Web Access</a></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="frames">
            <div class="frame" id="_grpmmb_">
                <table class="table hovered">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>IP Address / UserName</th>
                            <th>Group</th>
                            <th>Comment</th>
                            <th>&nbsp</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                    </tbody>
                    <tfoot>
                        <tr>
                            <th>&nbsp</th>
                            <th>&nbsp</th>
                            <th>&nbsp</th>
                            <th>
                                <input class="bg-anthilla-green fg-anthilla-gray upcase" type="button" value="Add" /></th>
                        </tr>
                    </tfoot>
                </table>
            </div>
            <div class="frame" id="_flip_">
                <table class="table hovered">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>IP Address</th>
                            <th>Comment</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <th>
                                <input type="text" />
                            </th>
                            <th>
                                <input type="text" />
                            </th>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                    <tfoot>
                        <tr>
                            <th>&nbsp</th>
                            <th>
                                <input class="bg-anthilla-green fg-anthilla-gray upcase" type="button" value="Add" /></th>
                        </tr>
                    </tfoot>
                </table>
            </div>
            <div class="frame" id="_flus_">
                <table class="table hovered">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>UserName</th>
                            <th>Comment</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <th>
                                <input type="text" />
                            </th>
                            <th>
                                <input type="text" />
                            </th>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                    <tfoot>
                        <tr>
                            <th>&nbsp</th>
                            <th>
                                <input class="bg-anthilla-green fg-anthilla-gray upcase" type="button" value="Add" /></th>
                        </tr>
                    </tfoot>
                </table>
            </div>
            <div class="frame" id="_waip_">
                <table class="table hovered">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>IP Address</th>
                            <th>Comment</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <th>
                                <input type="text" />
                            </th>
                            <th>
                                <input type="text" />
                            </th>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                    <tfoot>
                        <tr>
                            <th>&nbsp</th>
                            <th>
                                <input class="bg-anthilla-green fg-anthilla-gray upcase" type="button" value="Add" /></th>
                        </tr>
                    </tfoot>
                </table>
            </div>
            <div class="frame" id="_waus_">
                <table class="table hovered">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>UserName</th>
                            <th>Comment</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <th>
                                <input type="text" />
                            </th>
                            <th>
                                <input type="text" />
                            </th>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                    <tfoot>
                        <tr>
                            <th>&nbsp</th>
                            <th>
                                <input class="bg-anthilla-green fg-anthilla-gray upcase" type="button" value="Add" /></th>
                        </tr>
                    </tfoot>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <input class="bg-anthilla-green fg-anthilla-gray upcase" type="button" value="Apply Configuration" />
    <br />
    <legend>Temporal Access Lists</legend>
    <div class="tab-control" data-role="tab-control">
        <ul class="tabs">
            <li class="active"><a href="#_rules_">Rules</a></li>
            <li><a href="#_schdef_">Schedule Definition</a></li>
            <li><a href="#_ipass_">IP Association</a></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="frames">
            <div class="frame" id="_rules_"></div>
            <div class="frame" id="_schdef_"></div>
            <div class="frame" id="_ipass_"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br />
    <legend>Authentication Management</legend>
    <h5>Autenticazione Forzata</h5>
    <p>Enabled</p>
    <input type="radio" value="Yes" /><input type="radio" value="No" />
    <br />
    <p>
        Se abilitata il firewall richiederà nome utente e password per permettere la Navigazione.
le login e le password saranno quelle create nel menu gestione utenti del firewall.
configurazione consigliata per computer ad uso promiscuo.
NOTA: è necessario impostare nel browser dei clients l'uso del proxy IP 10.21.254.254 porta 8080
    </p>
    <br />
    <br />
    <h5>Autenticazione con Client IDENT</h5>
    <p>Enabled</p>
    <input type="radio" value="Yes" /><input type="radio" value="No" />
    <br />
    <p>
        Se abilitata il firewall contatterà tutti i computer che tenteranno di navigare.
loggando il nome utente in uso su quel computer e applicando le eventuali regole presenti per lo specifico utente.
configurazione consigliata per lan con dominio e computer in dotazione ad un solo utente .
NOTA: richiede l'utilizzo di un client IDENT sul personal computer
    </p>
    <br />
    <input class="bg-anthilla-green fg-anthilla-gray upcase" type="button" value="Save Configuration" />
    <input class="bg-anthilla-green fg-anthilla-gray upcase" type="button" value="Apply Configuration" />
